snippet.title: Valhalla (1983) - Gameplay
snippet.description:
Taken for The Adventurer's Guild:
https://advgamer.blogspot.com/
Gameplay from the ZX Spectrum/Commodore 64 adventure game Valhalla, in which you have to find six items for the Norse gods.
